---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base title="Contribute" description="Ways to contribute to Stratum.">
  <Nav />

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="mb-3 text-3xl font-bold text-stone-100">Contribute</h1>
    <p class="mb-16 max-w-2xl text-stone-400">
      Stratum is open source and free to use. There are a few ways to help, with or without writing code.
    </p>

    <div class="grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">

      <!-- Code -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-stone-800 bg-stone-900 p-7">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-stone-100">Code</h2>
        <p class="mb-5 text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
          Code contributions are welcome. Read the contributing guide before opening a PR - it covers the build setup, patch workflow, and what to include for performance work.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/StratumServer/Stratum/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="rounded-md bg-amber-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-stone-950 transition-colors hover:bg-amber-400"
          >
            Contributing guide
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/StratumServer/Stratum"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="rounded-md border border-stone-700 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-stone-300 transition-colors hover:border-stone-500 hover:bg-stone-800"
          >
            GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bug reports -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-stone-800 bg-stone-900 p-7">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-stone-100">Bug reports</h2>
        <p class="mb-5 text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
          Use the issue templates on GitHub. Before filing, check whether the problem also happens on a stock Vintage Story server - if it does, report it upstream.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/StratumServer/Stratum/issues/new/choose"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block rounded-md border border-stone-700 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-stone-300 transition-colors hover:border-stone-500 hover:bg-stone-800"
        >
          Open an issue
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Financial -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-stone-800 bg-stone-900 p-7">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-stone-100">Financial support</h2>
        <p class="mb-5 text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
          Stratum is built and maintained in spare time. If you want to support the project financially,
          Open Collective is the place. Every contribution helps keep development going.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://opencollective.com/stratum"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block rounded-md bg-amber-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-stone-950 transition-colors hover:bg-amber-400"
        >
          Support on Open Collective
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Community -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-stone-800 bg-stone-900 p-7">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-stone-100">Community</h2>
        <p class="mb-5 text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed">
          The Discord is where most of the day-to-day discussion happens. Helping other server owners get set up,
          sharing feedback, and reporting real-world behavior you observe on your server are all useful.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://discord.gg/pd24fawhsD"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block rounded-md border border-stone-700 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-stone-300 transition-colors hover:border-stone-500 hover:bg-stone-800"
        >
          Join Discord
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Security note -->
    <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl border border-stone-800 bg-stone-900/40 p-6">
      <h2 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-stone-100">Security issues</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-stone-400">
        Security vulnerabilities do not go in the issue tracker. See the
        <a href="https://github.com/StratumServer/Stratum/blob/main/SECURITY.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-amber-500 hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">security policy</a>
        for the reporting process.
      </p>
    </div>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Base>
